# מצאן — Caddy reverse-proxy config (committed template — NO secrets here).
#
# Caddy's job here is simple:
#   • Automatic HTTPS (Let's Encrypt certificate, auto-renewed)
#   • Forward traffic to the private dashboard (only Caddy can reach port 5050)
#
# The LOGIN is now handled by the app itself (a real login page + personal area
# per user), so Caddy no longer does Basic Auth.
#
# The only value it needs comes from .env on the server:
#   SITE_ADDRESS   your domain, e.g.  dironet.duckdns.org

{$SITE_ADDRESS} {
    reverse_proxy matzan:5050
}
